00:02:21.620 --> 00:02:22.730 align:middle line:90%
>>DOUILLARD: Who's left, really?

00:02:22.730 --> 00:02:23.090 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Right.

00:02:23.090 --> 00:02:24.980 align:middle line:84%
>>DOUILLARD: And this
is really an epidemic.

00:02:24.980 --> 00:02:27.022 align:middle line:84%
The experts believe the
next 10 years, everybody,

00:02:27.022 --> 00:02:29.360 align:middle line:84%
