00:02:29.360 --> 00:02:32.095 align:middle line:84%
but there's issues
taking place right now.

00:02:32.095 --> 00:02:33.470 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: I remember
an interview

00:02:33.470 --> 00:02:35.330 align:middle line:84%
I did about seven
years ago, and that

00:02:35.330 --> 00:02:37.520 align:middle line:84%
was the prognosis that
most of the population

00:02:37.520 --> 00:02:41.210 align:middle line:84%
