00:02:44.282 --> 00:02:45.740 align:middle line:84%
>>DOUILLARD: That's
actually right.

00:02:45.740 --> 00:02:48.920 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: So now,
first of all, I

00:02:48.920 --> 00:02:51.500 align:middle line:84%
would think that the symptoms
would be fairly obvious,

00:02:51.500 --> 00:02:53.150 align:middle line:90%
but you're saying they're not.

00:02:53.150 --> 00:02:54.890 align:middle line:90%
What are the symptoms?

00:02:54.890 --> 00:02:57.200 align:middle line:84%
>>DOUILLARD: They
are and they are not.

00:02:57.200 --> 00:03:00.800 align:middle line:84%
When this study came out
two years ago from the CDC,

00:03:00.800 --> 00:03:02.690 align:middle line:84%
