really quite simple.

00:26:34.440 --> 00:26:35.940 align:middle line:90%
Go back to basics.

00:26:35.940 --> 00:26:40.560 align:middle line:84%
Basics are three, good,
balanced meals per day.

00:26:40.560 --> 00:26:44.430 align:middle line:84%
