>>DOUILLARD: And what most
people don't realize is that

00:30:04.020 --> 00:30:07.680 align:middle line:84%
the blood sugar is
regulated by three things--

00:30:07.680 --> 00:30:10.950 align:middle line:84%
the efficiency of
your intestinal villi,

00:30:10.950 --> 00:30:16.470 align:middle line:84%
your pancreas, we all
know, and your liver.

00:30:16.470 --> 00:30:20.160 align:middle line:84%
And your liver might be the
most important one of all.

00:30:20.160 --> 00:30:22.470 align:middle line:84%
So when we hit it
with lots and lots

00:30:22.470 --> 00:30:27.300 align:middle line:84%
of sugars or lots of fructose,
then that overwhelms the liver.

00:30:27.300 --> 00:30:29.950 align:middle line:84%
Sugars are generally--
or fructose, for example,

00:30:29.950 --> 00:30:31.920 align:middle line:84%
is something that is
most commonly harvested

00:30:31.920 --> 00:30:33.300 align:middle line:90%
at the end of the summer.

00:30:33.300 --> 00:30:35.095 align:middle line:84%
The bears in the
fall are gorging

00:30:35.095 --> 00:30:37.470 align:middle line:84%
on apples and all the fruits
because it converts straight

00:30:37.470 --> 00:30:39.540 align:middle line:90%
into fat, so it insulates them.

00:30:39.540 --> 00:30:42.550 align:middle line:84%
And that's why nature gave
it to us, just to really help

00:30:42.550 --> 00:30:44.160 align:middle line:90%
to insulate and gain that fat.

00:30:44.160 --> 00:30:46.240 align:middle line:84%
So that's exactly
what fructose does.

00:30:46.240 --> 00:30:47.670 align:middle line:90%
It helps the body store fat.

00:30:47.670 --> 00:30:50.010 align:middle line:84%
It's not processed
very easily by liver.

00:30:50.010 --> 00:30:53.100 align:middle line:84%
It converts right into
fat as an insulator.

00:30:53.100 --> 00:30:55.240 align:middle line:90%
Once a year, not a bad deal.

00:30:55.240 --> 00:30:57.390 align:middle line:84%
But in our culture, when
we're doing that plus--

00:30:57.390 --> 00:30:57.720 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Every day.

00:30:57.720 --> 00:31:00.630 align:middle line:84%
>>DOUILLARD: --all the processed
sugars, and all the refined--

00:31:00.630 --> 00:31:02.640 align:middle line:84%
when you go to a
health food store,

00:31:02.640 --> 00:31:04.770 align:middle line:84%
