So then all of that food
at night just sits there,

00:38:57.560 --> 00:39:01.080 align:middle line:84%
and it's extremely hard
on the blood sugar.

00:39:01.080 --> 00:39:03.710 align:middle line:84%
So the Pitta body type,
the fiery body types, they

00:39:03.710 --> 00:39:07.010 align:middle line:84%
can definitely become diabetic
because they run the risk

00:39:07.010 --> 00:39:08.870 align:middle line:90%
