I really have about
Ayurveda, really

00:41:16.900 --> 00:41:19.280 align:middle line:84%
requires a different
kind of fuel as well.

00:41:19.280 --> 00:41:22.150 align:middle line:84%
A hypometabolism versus
a hypermetabolism

00:41:22.150 --> 00:41:25.300 align:middle line:84%
will be not only drawn to,
but require different types

00:41:25.300 --> 00:41:26.812 align:middle line:90%
of food, won't they?

00:41:26.812 --> 00:41:28.270 align:middle line:84%
So I would like to
go through this.

00:41:28.270 --> 00:41:30.080 align:middle line:84%
And aren't most of us
a combination of them?

00:41:30.080 --> 00:41:31.180 align:middle line:90%
>>DOUILLARD: Yeah, we are.

00:41:31.180 --> 00:41:32.530 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: We have a
dominant, but we'll

00:41:32.530 --> 00:41:34.842 align:middle line:84%
have a little bit of one,
or maybe both of the others.

00:41:34.842 --> 00:41:35.800 align:middle line:90%
>>DOUILLARD: It's true.

00:41:35.800 --> 00:41:38.590 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: OK, so let's
take a dominant Vata

00:41:38.590 --> 00:41:40.300 align:middle line:90%
type of personality.

00:41:40.300 --> 00:41:43.240 align:middle line:84%
What would a day of
eating look like for them?

00:41:43.240 --> 00:41:46.120 align:middle line:84%
The foods that would really
benefit their disposition,

00:41:46.120 --> 00:41:47.918 align:middle line:90%
their body type.

00:41:47.918 --> 00:41:49.960 align:middle line:84%
>>DOUILLARD: One of the
risks of a Vata body type

00:41:49.960 --> 00:41:53.560 align:middle line:84%
is they are very sensitive,
and they have super high radar,

00:41:53.560 --> 00:41:55.180 align:middle line:90%
so they feel everything.

