And they have a very
sensitive system,

00:42:02.380 --> 00:42:05.870 align:middle line:84%
so they don't have a real
robust digestive system.

00:42:05.870 --> 00:42:07.990 align:middle line:84%
So they're the
first ones to have

00:42:07.990 --> 00:42:11.230 align:middle line:84%
issues with harder to digest
foods, like wheat and dairy,

00:42:11.230 --> 00:42:12.790 align:middle line:90%
or animal products.

00:42:12.790 --> 00:42:14.710 align:middle line:84%
So they're the first
ones to get rid of wheat,

00:42:14.710 --> 00:42:16.502 align:middle line:84%
and they get rid of
dairy, and they get rid

00:42:16.502 --> 00:42:17.470 align:middle line:90%
of animal products.

00:42:17.470 --> 00:42:19.750 align:middle line:84%
And they're the ones to
shift towards being more ve--

00:42:19.750 --> 00:42:20.770 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Because they're
more hypersensitive.

00:42:20.770 --> 00:42:21.895 align:middle line:84%
>>DOUILLARD: Yeah, so
they become vegetarians.

00:42:21.895 --> 00:42:22.180 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: OK.

00:42:22.180 --> 00:42:23.100 align:middle line:84%
>>DOUILLARD: And for
all good reasons.

00:42:23.100 --> 00:42:25.433 align:middle line:84%
I don't want to eat animals
and all these great reasons.

00:42:25.433 --> 00:42:28.030 align:middle line:84%
The problem is that those
are dense proteins that

00:42:28.030 --> 00:42:29.750 align:middle line:90%
stabilize blood sugar.

