So if that Vata body
type became a vegetarian

00:42:32.350 --> 00:42:35.703 align:middle line:84%
because they didn't digest
those hard to digest foods well

00:42:35.703 --> 00:42:37.870 align:middle line:84%
because they were very
sensitive in their digestion,

00:42:37.870 --> 00:42:40.328 align:middle line:84%
and we didn't fix the reason,
and we just went to an easier

00:42:40.328 --> 00:42:43.960 align:middle line:84%
