become lousy vegetarians.

00:42:43.960 --> 00:42:46.810 align:middle line:84%
And how you become
a lousy vegetarian?

00:42:46.810 --> 00:42:48.730 align:middle line:84%
Without good protein
or enough protein,

00:42:48.730 --> 00:42:50.017 align:middle line:90%
you start to crave sugar.

00:42:50.017 --> 00:42:51.100 align:middle line:90%
You start to crave sweets.

