In Ayurveda, it's
interesting, there

00:43:17.200 --> 00:43:19.690 align:middle line:84%
are six tastes-- sweet,
sour, salt, pungent, bitter,

00:43:19.690 --> 00:43:20.650 align:middle line:90%
and astringent.

00:43:20.650 --> 00:43:23.650 align:middle line:84%
And in America, we live
on sweet, sour, and salt.

00:43:23.650 --> 00:43:25.620 align:middle line:84%
And sweet, sour, and
salt are comfort foods.

00:43:25.620 --> 00:43:26.610 align:middle line:90%
They calm us down.

00:43:26.610 --> 00:43:30.310 align:middle line:84%
McDonald's-- he must've went
to India many years ago,

