The other three tastes--

00:44:03.370 --> 00:44:06.190 align:middle line:84%
bitter, and pungent, and
astringent-- the greens,

00:44:06.190 --> 00:44:08.470 align:middle line:84%
and the spicy foods,
and those bitter roots

00:44:08.470 --> 00:44:10.160 align:middle line:84%
that just aren't in
our diet anymore,

00:44:10.160 --> 00:44:12.250 align:middle line:84%
those are the ones that
balance our blood sugar.

