toxic chemicals,

00:45:15.070 --> 00:45:17.890 align:middle line:84%
are circulating in your
blood, damaging and irritating

00:45:17.890 --> 00:45:20.230 align:middle line:84%
your arteries, and
causing the predisposition

00:45:20.230 --> 00:45:21.950 align:middle line:90%
to heart disease.

00:45:21.950 --> 00:45:25.060 align:middle line:84%
So the vegetables are
what escort the toxins

00:45:25.060 --> 00:45:26.170 align:middle line:90%
into the toilet.

00:45:26.170 --> 00:45:28.150 align:middle line:84%
Not enough of those,
they go right back.

